  <description type="morphology">Stems 20–80 cm, mostly unbranched, glabrous. Leaves bicolor (white and green); blades lanceolate to ovate, 5–7 × 0.5–1 cm, irregularly pinnatifid; abaxial faces tomentose (abaxial) or glabrate (adaxial). Involucres campanulate, 2–3 × 2–3 mm. Heads in paniculiform or racemiform arrays 10–15 × 2–6 cm. Florets: pistillate ca. 10; bisexual 3–8; corollas 2 mm.</description>
  <description type="phenology">Flowering mid–late summer.</description>
